page.content: BROWNIES AND GUIDES WE HAVE BROWNIES AT HAREWOOD C.OF E.PRIMARY SCHOOL. OUR BROWN OWL IS MRS FRANKLAND AND OUR BADGER IS MRS SUTCLIFFE.WE HAVE 3 SIXES,THE ELVES, THE PIXIES AND THE GNOMES.WE PLAY GAMES,DO INTEREST BADGES,SING SONGS AND DANCE ROUND THE TOADSTOOL.WE GO ON A PACK HOLIDAY EACH YEAR.WE HAVE A GUIDE PACK IN HAREWOOD TOO,BUT THERE ARE ONLY 3 GUIDES.WE JOIN WITH THE BROWNIES.AT THE END OF THE MEETING WE SING'TAP' DAY IS DONE GONE THE SUN FROM THE SEA FROM THE SKY FROM THE HILLS ALL IS WELL SAFELY RESTS GOD IS NIGH
